"""Test that adding arms with variance causes a ValueError."""
historical_info = copy.deepcopy(self.
    three_arms_with_variance_no_unsampled_arm_test_case)
with pytest.raises(ValueError):
    historical_info.append_sample_arms(self.
        three_arms_with_variance_no_unsampled_arm_test_case.arms_sampled)
